==English==

===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|whatever}}; equivalent to {{af|en|what|ever}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|RP}} {{IPA|en|/ʍɒtˈɛvə/|/wɒtˈɛvə/}}
* {{a|GA}} {{IPA|en|/wʌtˈɛvɚ/|/wəɾˈɛvɚ/}}
* {{audio|en|En-us-whatever.ogg|Audio (GA)}}
* {{rhymes|en|ɛvə(ɹ)|s=3}}

The {{IPAchar|/t/}} in {{m|en|whatever}} may be [[w:Flapping|flapped]] in certain dialects despite the fact that the {{IPAchar|/t/}} precedes a stressed vowel due to the morpheme boundary between {{m|en|what}} and {{m|en|-ever}}.

